@startuml
actor Client
participant "quotes.views.get_driverscore" as API
participant "quotes.views.get_driver_score" as get_driver_score

Client -> API: POST /get_driverscore (violations, lockrate, ignore_lock_rate_for_points)
API -> API: json.loads(request.body)
API -> API: Extract violations_data, lock_rate_date, ignore_lock_rate_for_points
API -> get_driver_score: get_driver_score(violations_data, lock_rate_date, ignore_lock_rate_for_points)
get_driver_score --> API: points
API -> API: Build response dict
API -> Client: Response({points}, HTTP 200)
@enduml